<p><persName>Mr. Mills M Battles</persName></p>

<p>To<persName> J. and J Austin</persName>&#8212;                                                               Dr.</p>

<p>To 10 lbs Coffee Sent by <persName>Barret </persName>@ 4/c  [four bits]------- 5.00</p>

<p>15   To  20   lb   Ditto   @   4/c-----------------------10.00</p>

<p>To 16 lbs. Suger e. 2/c-----------------------------------4.00</p>

<p>To Your order on <persName>S. F. Austin</persName>----------------------------$19.00</p>

<p>7.12 1/2</p>

<p>$26.12 1/2</p>
<p>Deduct 2 lbs.  coffee-------------------------------------  1. 00</p>

